	<div id="prg-wrapper-featured"><!-- START MAIN CONTENT AREA -->
	<div class="box top_promo">
	<div class="header"><h1>Experimenting on animals</h1>
	
	</div>
	<div class="content">
	<p>Animal experiments are widely used to develop new medicines and to test the safety of other products. Many of these experiments cause pain to the animals involved or reduce their quality of life in other ways. If it is morally wrong to cause animals to suffer then experimenting on animals produces serious moral problems.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="footer"> </div>
	</div>
		
	<div class="p-grp p-grp-a p-grp-theme-n nth-row-n">
	<!--LEFT HAND NAV-->
